{"tid":1562450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：泛民現在帶你高唱港獨國歌，引誘你進入夢遺，預支未來的政治高潮射精出水，目的就是要你精盡人亡囉","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:19:43.000Z","uid":133680,"like":12,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7b18179769f25e330c752bf1f85ab124a442c524","tid":1562450,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"陳雲：今天我。在香港人在地產商的幫助下，在各個商場高唱《願榮光歸香港》自high香港獨立有國歌的時候，共產黨派泛民去美國遊說擱置法案審議，中共也派出黑金遊說團去接觸美國參議員。<br />\n中共非常之明白香港人的自卑自戀與高傲自大，會準確地餵食興奮劑，令香港人迷醉於遙遠的夢幻歡樂。例如未普選之前夢想香港獨立，有得在地產商的商場自由高唱香港國歌。<br />\n美國國會復會之前，林鄭月娥口說會正式撤回修訂，令議案要對付的濫用引渡的惡劣情景不再存在。熟悉美國議會的學者告知，只要有一位參議員被泛民或中共或兩者一齊打動，擱置議案（hold），擱置議案如果沒有三分之二的議員反對，議案將胎死腹中，石沉大海。<br />\n泛民一再放出不要經濟制裁香港的言論，也可以令到法案在審議的時候被解除武裝，變成一個無層級制裁選項（一個一個高官點名懲罰）的香港民主支持法案，最終令法案沒有約束力。<br />\n泛民的支持者在商場高唱香港國歌的時候，泛民、黃之鋒等人就在美國做這些遊說。<br />\n泛民一向反對港獨，現在帶你高唱港獨國歌，引誘你進入夢遺，預支未來的政治高潮射精出水，目的就是要你精盡人亡囉。<br />\n（陳雲之鹹濕論政。）"},{"pid":"daef3ba1997a51fb43fdc9b95657f3d2033cb221","tid":1562450,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3eba2ae66736206a0f1585a4e01037b95e29cca1","tid":1562450,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45d7729adffe03123786add30bd9cc4954ad82bf","tid":1562450,"uid":67813,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"好L煩個老野"},{"pid":"95040d915d92d55ece6d45edfd18b81b7da941d4","tid":1562450,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"泛民作架咩首野"},{"pid":"6c90a46a6f2819e166af4d99847961cf4335e336","tid":1562450,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"如果係唱城邦會戰勝歸來，國師就會話勝利在望"},{"pid":"5cb7705b4ed1974a2a6056da7ca6a0538db5a785","tid":1562450,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"煩過唐僧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a156c4a72f2adc15c5dfe379bb2789ed5d75fc","tid":1562450,"uid":14912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"食左春藥"},{"pid":"c997d97417a8505fe9c239f457aa6e11a2119ad4","tid":1562450,"uid":29311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"食藥啦仆街"},{"pid":"d676ae9eca45d3c6ec8adb948b1b585d224d9f20","tid":1562450,"uid":7818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6c90a46a6f2819e166af4d99847961cf4335e336","tid":1562450,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"如果係唱城邦會戰勝歸來，國師就會話勝利在望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"如果唱城邦會戰勝歸來<br />\n就變左國師射精射出水，精盡人亡<br />\n怨婦陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d07dc87facb249097579271a03925a637e0ef4","tid":1562450,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c90a46a6f2819e166af4d99847961cf4335e336","tid":1562450,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"如果係唱城邦會戰勝歸來，國師就會話勝利在望"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"快d同葉留結婚，好狠煩。<br />\n贏到先內鬥啦，白痴國師"}